name: XMEME
description: How It Started Born in November 2023, XMEME is the OG memecoin of the XRPL, blending humor, community, and blockchain brilliance. From its humble beginnings, it’s grown into the #1 memecoin on the ledger, powered by a passionate community that knows how to have fun while breaking boundaries. XMEME isn’t just a token—it’s a movement. A little humor, a lot of ambition, and endless potential. This is where memes meet the future of finance.
